            "text" : "I do not know what they will bring.  It would be hard to diagnose a solution with a replacement when they did not even check to see if the DVR was the issue.  T We ask that you please send your general availability for the appointment and your best contact number/email so that contact can be made the day before, the day of, and when we are en route. ^MJS",
