            "recipientId" : "19638927",
            "reactions" : [ ],
            "urls" : [ ],
            "text" : "When I last ordered a service call, They told me they didn't have any replacements available. I'd appreciate any help getting me a new one brought to me. This has been a quite frustrating and disappointing experience. I'll likely terminate my account as soon as I can figure out how to NCAA &amp; NFL football w/o cable or satellite.",
