            "recipientId" : "19638927",
            "reactions" : [ ],
            "urls" : [ ],
            "text" : "Ok thank you confirming that. I look forward to the update. Is there anything you can do to help me either get a replacement DVR ASAP, or credit my account for the interim? It doesn't feel fair to pay full price for less than full service.",
